products.title: FINNALA Sofa, Gunnared beige
products.description: The FINNALA threeseater sofa in Gunnared beige is a customizable sectional that can be built in different configurations to fit your space. It features pocketspring seat cushions with highresilience polyurethane foam and a top layer of polyester wadding for lasting comfort and support. The cover is made from dopedyed Gunnared fabric  100 % polyester (minimum 90 % recycled) with a woollike feel and a twotone melange effect  and is removable and machinewashable. The frame combines plywood, particleboard, solid wood, fiberboard and polypropylene legs, while the armrest and crossrail use steel with an epoxy/polyester powder coating. The sofa comes with a 10year limited warranty, softwashable cover, and a range of optional accessories. Dimensions (overall): Width 241 cm, Depth 98 cm, Height including back cushions 85 cm, Backrest height 71 cm, Height under furniture 6 cm. Seat width 211 cm, Seat depth 55 cm, Seat height 48 cm, Armrest width 15 cm, Armrest height 71 cm. Article Number (SKU): 393.190.59. Price: $999.00 (reduced from $1,349.00).
